@startuml component_architecture
!theme plain

title UIM Audit Log Service - Component Architecture

actor "SAP BTP App/Service" as Producer
actor "Compliance Auditor" as Auditor

node "Audit Log Service Runtime" {
  component "AuditLogServer\n(vibe.d REST API)" as Api
  component "AuditLogService\n(Write/Retrieve/Viewer/Retention)" as Domain
  database "AuditLogStore\n(In-Memory Audit Events)" as Store
}

Producer --> Api : Write API (OAuth2 token)
Auditor --> Api : Retrieval API + Viewer
Api --> Domain : route + validate
Domain --> Store : persist/read/purge

note right of Domain
Features:
- recommended event types
- retrieval + download preview
- viewer for subaccount logs
- default 90-day retention
- premium retention and cost estimate
end note

@enduml
